This change required adjustments to both the control logic and enclosure design, resulting in a more compact and integrated structure.

The App

The mobile application simplifies device setup and pairing. Instead of requiring manual network configuration, the app manages device provisioning, Wi-Fi setup, and pairing within a single interface.

